- Enters area, can continue following the path across the first bridge

- Can look immediately right, and realize he doesn't need to cross bridges at all,
and just exit the area

- If walks left, can run into the ocean, and fight a big fish (if there is 
a big fish)

- Encounters and fights "Jack of the bridge", who explains that due to a previous
bridge experiencing failure, they introduced redundancy by building two
bridges 

- Encounters "Redundant Jack of the bridge", who exists on the redundant bridge

- Can exit area and head towards city